node.text:
The biggest animal on Earth via @adam_ernster. 🐋 Apply for a feature following the link in our bio and we will publish your photos in our account: @adventurefervor

Blue Whales can hold their breath for about 90 minutes, reaching a maximum length of 100 feet or 30 metres long and weight up to 200 tons, it is the largest animal known to have ever existed... 🤯

This video was taken in the Santa Barbara Channel where over 27 different types of whales and dolphins call this place home, making these waters one of the best whale watching areas in the world.

From May to September you can see Blue Whales, Minke Whales and Humpback Whales. Occasionally, you can see Right Whales or Orcas. All season long you have an excellent chance of seeing dolphins, porpoises, seals and sea lions.

Who would you share this experience with? 🐳

📽 @condorexpresssb & @adam_ernster
📍 Santa Barbara, California, USA
🎶 Thomas Newman - Wow

Tag a book lover! 😌 Share your photos with us and we will post them in our account. Apply for a feature following the link in our bio: @adventurefervor

Reading is important because it develops the mind. Understanding the written word is one way the mind grows in its ability. Teaching young children to read helps them develop their language skills. It also helps them learn to listen.

When you read, you exercise your comprehension abilities and your analytical abilities. It fires up your imagination and stimulates the memory centers of your mind. It helps recall information as well as stabilize your emotions. The importance of a reading habit is that it strengthens mental muscles.

📽 @lulumoonowlbooks
🎶 Aspidistrafly - Landscape With a Fairy

This fiery New York sunset via @cmonlevad is where our minds are currently at. 😌 💭 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on adventurefervor.com (link in my bio: @adventurefervor)

If you love riding your bike, you’ll be glad to do it and try the experience in New York City. 🌤

The exact location this was recorded in is at Central Park West and West 72nd Street. If you're thinking about a trip to New York City, a bike ride is among the best ways to explore the area. You can drive at you own pace, explore at will, and spend as much time as you want in any particular place. With New York City being one of the best US destinations to explore, biking in NYC makes the experience a blast! 🗽

Who would you enjoy a ride in NYC with? 🇺🇸

📽 @cmonlevad
📍 New York City, USA
🎶 90sFlav - Call me
